build.md
     1в†’# The build command
     3в†’The build command is used to render your book:
     4в†’
     5в†’```bash
     6в†’mdbook build
     7в†’```
     8в†’
     9в†’It will try to parse your `SUMMARY.md` file to understand the structure of your
    10в†’book and fetch the corresponding files. Note that this will also create files
    11в†’mentioned in `SUMMARY.md` which are not yet present.
    12в†’
    13в†’The rendered output will maintain the same directory structure as the source for
    14в†’convenience. Large books will therefore remain structured when rendered.
    15в†’
